    <h2>3. The black-tie</h2>

    <p>The Mira goes black-tie with the right styling. Try the long-sleeve version in midnight. Add the Heritage Silk Scarf as a stole, dramatic earrings, and our highest pair of heels. Skip the belt — the dress is the point.</p>

    <p>This is the version we tested at a wedding last month. Nobody asked where it was from. Everybody asked who it was from.</p>

    <hr class="journal-post__divider" />

    <p class="journal-post__close">The Mira comes in five colours — oat, silver, midnight, champagne and ink — and four sizes (XS–L). Made in Kuwait, in batches of 40. There are 17 left in oat as of this morning.</p>

